545
00:33:39,050 --> 00:33:40,176
They're not the enemy.

546
00:33:41,085 --> 00:33:43,918
Besides, they do have a point,
don't they?

547
00:33:44,088 --> 00:33:46,579
I did screw up.

548
00:33:47,058 --> 00:33:48,992
Okay.

549
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,855
Just so you know, it's your call.

550
00:33:55,433 --> 00:33:57,060
Drink this.

551
00:33:57,235 --> 00:33:59,897
It'll make you feel better.

552
00:34:06,444 --> 00:34:08,344
You're frightened.

553
00:34:08,513 --> 00:34:11,710
It's all right, I understand.
But you don't have to be.

554
00:34:11,883 --> 00:34:13,783
