- What?

565
00:35:37,835 --> 00:35:40,269
It's those butterflies.

566
00:35:40,438 --> 00:35:43,464
They're in Maia's journals.
She's here.

567
00:35:55,686 --> 00:35:57,620
All right, let's go. Secure the area.

568
00:36:11,002 --> 00:36:12,663
Maia.

569
00:36:20,678 --> 00:36:22,373
- What is going on?
- Don't move!

570
00:36:24,215 --> 00:36:25,204
Please.

571
00:36:25,383 --> 00:36:29,410
Please, this house is for sale,
