580
00:37:11,996 --> 00:37:13,486
You're in the future.

581
00:37:14,932 --> 00:37:18,129
We had to bring you here, Maia.
You and your friends.

582
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:21,231
We need your help.

583
00:37:29,213 --> 00:37:31,738
It'll all be over soon.

584
00:37:31,916 --> 00:37:34,077
