597
00:38:23,167 --> 00:38:25,397
Come on, I'll take you home.

598
00:38:41,519 --> 00:38:43,316
Sign here.

599
00:38:44,689 --> 00:38:46,919
Can you sign here?

600
00:38:48,826 --> 00:38:49,884
Thank you, Shawn.

601
00:38:50,061 --> 00:38:52,461
I know this wasn't an easy decision.

602
00:38:59,403 --> 00:39:01,394
Yeah, well,

603
00:39:01,572 --> 00:39:04,370
