613
00:39:38,876 --> 00:39:41,037
Nothing happened.

614
00:39:41,212 --> 00:39:42,406
There wasn't an earthquake.

615
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:44,511
I didn't melt.

616
00:39:45,116 --> 00:39:47,311
I used to be scared of you.

617
00:39:47,485 --> 00:39:49,783
But I don't think you have
any power over me at all, do you?

618
00:40:08,038 --> 00:40:09,300
I didn't think so.

619
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:13,438
I'll do my own shopping
from now on, okay?

620
00:40:20,317 --> 00:40:23,582
Okay, sweetheart,
we're ready to begin.

621
00:40:23,754 --> 00:40:26,154
Don't cry.

622
00:40:26,924 --> 00:40:28,949
You and the other children
we took,

