638
00:41:08,732 --> 00:41:10,393
we'll make you forget your mother,

639
00:41:10,568 --> 00:41:13,560
Marco and your friends.

640
00:41:13,737 --> 00:41:16,729
- Please, don't.
- They'll forget you too.

641
00:41:17,007 --> 00:41:18,975
